title: Norton Internet Security 2013 20.4.0.40 + Trial Reset
description:
Norton Internet Security 2013 20.4.0.40 + Trial Reset

Instructions:

1. Reboot in Safe Mode
2. Open NTR2013 and click convert
3. System will then restart and you should have 180 days

OR

1. Settings - General - Product Security
2. Turn Off Norton Product Tamper Protection
3. Apply
4. Select the duration Permanently 
5. OK
6. Then click convert

If it's expired, remove it and install this one
